  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We have herein analysed the patients admitted to our Department that underwent serologic
      tests for SARS-CoV-2 either by Ab or RT PCR, to estimate the prevalence of COVID-19 in the
      setting of a non-dedicated COVID-19 hospital and in a low CoV-2 incidence area, and to
      evaluate if security measures are necessary for this context.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
